commitResults.messageBody:
This changes argument tokenization such that it will parse all flags
with the matching default syntax and any explicitly specified flags.

Additionally, whitespace must now surround the flags for them to be
valid.

Extra convenience methods are added to simplify new operations that
can be useful for commands thanks to this refactor.

commitResults.messageBody:
The tokenizer will now automatically tokenize flags that are not
explicitly given, as long as it matches the default syntax. Thus, we
add a new test to explicitly cover this behavior.
